.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL_FORCE_CLOSE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-force-close \- unilaterally close a channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-force-close
.I channel_id
.SH DESCRIPTION
Initiates a unilateral (force) close of the specified channel.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
